It's real data, and it's somewhat interesting, especially if you fly into New York City.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:38.519
So when it comes to accessing information in your data frame, it can help to just extract

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:44.040
information that's already there to avoid the sort of overwhelming amounts of distraction

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:49.040
