00:09:36.059 --> 00:09:40.659
give it a second or third variable, a range will use that variable as a tiebreaker variable

00:09:40.659 --> 00:09:47.119
within rows that have the same values of preceding variables. So you can see here that by adding

00:09:47.119 --> 00:09:52.460
date as a tiebreaker, the order of Alex and Arthur changes, even though Alex and Arthur

00:09:52.460 --> 00:10:02.979
both had a wind speed of 45, the date of Arthur comes before the date of Alex. Okay,

