So I know it's been a lot. This is definitely going to be a whirlwind tour, but we're near

00:18:44.219 --> 00:18:49.540
the end. You can extract variables and observations with Select and Filter. You can rearrange

00:18:49.540 --> 00:18:54.900
your data with Arrange. You can make new variables with Mutate, and you can make new observations

00:18:54.900 --> 00:18:59.819
on new units of analysis by combining Group By with Summarize.

00:18:59.819 --> 00:19:03.900
Thanks for checking out our data wrangling video series. This is just one video in a

